data.description: Introducing this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bath pool home in Port St. John, Florida, a hidden gem in Brevard County. This home has recently undergone a stunning renovation, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. The open floor plan kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring elegant granite countertops, custom 42'' wood cabinets, and modern stainless steel appliances. Both bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled and plumbing fully updated. The living area with vaulted ceilings boasts new ''wood'' tile flooring, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step out onto the screened porch or covered patio to enjoy the view of the spacious in-ground pool. Convenience is key, with easy access to Interstate 195 for quick trips to the beach, Kennedy Space Center, the Port, and Orlando. Plus, the open space across the street ensures added privacy. This property is sure to be in high demand, with a large, newly fenced yard, a heated pool, and spa. Roof, plumbing, and water heater are brand NEW (2023). The sale includes washer, dryer, and all kitchen stainless steel appliances, as well as an outdoor bar, grill, and mini fridge will convey. Modern interior doors, knockdown ceilings, and recessed interior lighting add the finishing touch. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity, especially if you're looking for a residence in the Challenger Seven & Space Coast Jr/Sr High School District and the Cocoa community.
